│                                                                                                                                            │
│ Then substitute into KE:                                                                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                                            │
│ $$                                                                                                                                         │
│ T_K = \frac{1}{2} m \cdot \dot{x}^2 = \frac{1}{2} m \cdot \left( \frac{p}{m} \right)^2 = \frac{1}{2} \cdot \frac{p^2}{m^2} \cdot m^2 = \fr│
│                                                                                                                                            │
│ Wait:                                                                                                                                      │
