│ Wait, hold on — this is critical.                                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                          │
│ Confusion arises because:                                                                                                                │
│                                                                                                                                          │
│ There exists two distinct objects: the **actual** momentum (not denoted in boldface), and the **derived** derivative.                    │
│                                                                                                                                          │
│ But according to standard textbook conventions, the **canonical momentum** is typically defined as:                                      │
│                                                                                                                                          │
│ $$                                                                                                                                       │
│ p_j = \frac{\partial L}{\partial \dot{q}_j} \Rightarrow \text{standard definition}                                                       │
│ $$                                                                                                                                       │
│                                                                                                                                          │
│ Yet in our current setup, we've been mixing notions too early.                                                                           │
│                                                                                                                                          │
│ Let’s try this cleaner route:                                                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                                          │
