│    $$                                                                                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                           │
│    Note: Only if x is **positive** downward.                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                                           │
│ ✅ So, combine them fully:                                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                           │
│ $$                                                                                                                                        │
│ V = V_s + V_g = 3x^2 + 29.4x                                                                                                              │
│ $$                                                                                                                                        │
